Package: HACSim
Type: Package
Title: Iterative Extrapolation of Species' Haplotype Accumulation
        Curves for Genetic Diversity Assessment
Version: 1.0.7-1
Date: 2025-09-17
Authors@R: c(person(given = c("Jarrett", "D."),
